        h1 Cookie Policy

        h2 1. What Are Cookies?
        p Cookies are small text files that are placed on your device by websites that you visit. They are widely used to make websites work more efficiently, as well as to provide information to the site owners.

        h2 2. How We Use Cookies
        p We use cookies to enhance your experience on GrooveGrid. Cookies help us:
        ul
          li Understand how you use our website
          li Personalize your experience
          li Remember your preferences and settings
          li Analyze site traffic and improve our services

        h2 3. Types of Cookies We Use
        p We use the following types of cookies on GrooveGrid:
        ul
          li
            strong Essential Cookies:
            |  These cookies are necessary for the website to function properly.
          li
            strong Performance Cookies:
            |  These cookies help us understand how visitors interact with our website by providing information on the pages visited and time spent on the site.
          li
            strong Functionality Cookies:
            |  These cookies remember your preferences and customize the user experience accordingly.
          li
            strong Targeting/Advertising Cookies:
            |  These cookies are used to deliver relevant ads to users based on their browsing behavior.

        h2 4. Managing Your Cookies
        p You can control and manage cookies through your browser settings. Most browsers allow you to refuse cookies or to alert you when a cookie is being placed on your device. However, if you disable cookies, some parts of GrooveGrid may not function properly.

        h2 5. Changes to This Cookie Policy
        p We may update this Cookie Policy from time to time to reflect changes in our practices or for other operational, legal, or regulatory reasons. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we use cookies.

        h2 6. Contact Us
        p If you have any questions about our use of cookies, please contact us at groovegrid@org.com

